![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578252112148-0TOXVECG5YTPVHL4C7C3/image-asset.jpeg)

DC is at bat yet again, this time taking a swing at a  character most are unfamiliar with...Shazam! The 2019 film is already making waves since opening this weekend, but was it any good? Check in with The Clique as we recap and review Shazam starring Asher Angel, Zachary Levi and Mark Strong, a film that definitely made us wish we were punk kids again. Ah those were the days.

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
